Description: # Wok
        
        `wok-serve` is a tool to serve a directory of Wok files as a website using a Notion-like template.
        
        Example usage:
        
        ```bash
        # Show help
        wok-serve -h
        
        # Serve a directory
        wok-serve -d my_files/
        
        # Listen on a custom host/port
        wok-serve -d my_files/ --host 0.0.0.0 --port 8000
        ```
        
